967
01:23:25,740 --> 01:23:29,870
你想帮忙便爬上直升机指挥机师
You want to help? Climb up that ladder and commandeer that helo.

968
01:23:29,960 --> 01:23:32,030
你疯了吗?爬上去?
Are you crazy? Climb up there?

969
01:23:32,170 --> 01:23:33,740
可能会失败 但试试看
It might not work, but try.

970
01:23:33,840 --> 01:23:34,830
你去哪儿?
Where are you going?

971
01:23:34,920 --> 01:23:35,790
那女孩
The girl.

972
01:23:36,380 --> 01:23:39,000
宁静 这是麻雀
Tranquility, this is Sparrow. I'm in position. Over.

973
01:23:39,090 --> 01:23:42,290
这是宁静 照计划保持原位
This is Tranquility. Hold position as planned. Out.

974
01:23:48,060 --> 01:23:50,050
把梯子移近一点
Hey, bring that ladder closer.

975
01:23:50,230 --> 01:23:52,800
你看不见我想做英雄吗?
Can't you see I'm trying to be a hero?

976
01:23:54,980 --> 01:23:56,260
这样才是
That's better.

977
01:24:02,990 --> 01:24:06,070
这是麻雀 已接了第一个人
This is Sparrow. We made our first pickup.

978
01:24:06,410 --> 01:24:09,410
你没有 快上去应付吧
The hell you have. Get up there and deal with that.

979
01:24:41,190 --> 01:24:42,770
什么回事?
What's going on?

980
01:24:47,700 --> 01:24:49,030
揍他吧!
Kick his butt!

981
01:24:59,670 --> 01:25:02,240
我们教他怎样飞
Honey, we sure taught that boy how to fly.

982
01:25:02,800 --> 01:25:03,960
是的
We sure did.

983
01:25:04,300 --> 01:25:07,140
现在把直升机停留在这儿
Now we're going to keep this chopper right here.

984
01:25:07,600 --> 01:25:11,640
否则便杀了你 你明白吗?
Or I'm going to blow your brains out! You got that, honey?

985
01:26:28,760 --> 01:26:30,800
让我杀了雷贝克
Let me handle Ryback.

986
01:26:31,850 --> 01:26:34,010
你应付技技方面的事
You take care of the techno shit.

987
01:26:35,310 --> 01:26:36,890
他是我的
He's mine.

988
01:26:39,770 --> 01:26:42,060
我亲手杀了他
I'll take him myself, hand to hand.

989
01:26:42,570 --> 01:26:47,140
我的假卫星你们要掩掩我的宝贝
Come on my little ghost satellites, I need you with me to hide my baby...

990
01:26:47,320 --> 01:26:49,990
好让它把华府炸个稀烂
...so she can blow the fuck out of Washington.

991
01:26:50,910 --> 01:26:52,900
你去送死吧
Go get your throat ripped out.

992
01:26:53,240 --> 01:26:57,160
我要杀八百万人和去拿十亿元
I got eight million people to kill, and one billion dollars to pick up.

993
01:27:03,170 --> 01:27:04,580
谢谢
Thank you, sir.

994
01:27:04,920 --> 01:27:07,330
总统等人已疏散了
The President and staff have been evacuated.

995
01:27:07,920 --> 01:27:11,420
若不能阻止会有百万计的人死亡
Leaving millions of innocent people to die if we don't stop it.

996
01:27:11,510 --> 01:27:13,500
现在要用科学卫星了
We must use Pegasus now.

997
01:27:13,930 --> 01:27:15,180
但是
But, sir...

998
01:27:18,230 --> 01:27:20,550
仍有八个可能性
...we still have eight possibilities.

999
01:27:23,230 --> 01:27:24,430
选一个吧
Pick one.

1000
01:27:26,650 --> 01:27:27,680
快!
Now!

1001
01:27:29,450 --> 01:27:30,360
K吧
Kappa.

1002
01:27:30,450 --> 01:27:34,200
谢谢 目标是K 准备发射
Thank you. Kappa's the target. Stand by and launch.

1003
01:27:39,540 --> 01:27:41,950
我从不害怕任何人
I've never been afraid of anybody.

1004
01:27:43,130 --> 01:27:45,280
但你的叔叔使我害怕
But that uncle of yours scares me.

1005
01:27:49,300 --> 01:27:50,960
我喜欢
And I like it.

1006
01:28:41,020 --> 01:28:43,340
你和我打 否则我和她同归于尽
It's you and me... or me and her.

1007
01:29:05,380 --> 01:29:09,500
你要抓紧否则粉身碎骨
Now, you hold on real tight and you'll stay in one piece.

1008
01:29:54,420 --> 01:29:56,220
你弄破我的外衣
Fuck, you ruined my coat.

1009
01:30:07,060 --> 01:30:08,260
早安
Good morning.

1010
01:31:51,300 --> 01:31:52,230
起来

1011
01:32:01,380 --> 01:32:03,540
从没有人在厨房能胜过我
Nobody beats me in the kitchen.

1012
01:32:12,650 --> 01:32:17,400
我走了 我不需要这些 我要的
I must go. Won't need any of this anymore. Everything I need...

1013
01:32:17,730 --> 01:32:19,060
在这儿
...is right here.

1014
01:32:19,150 --> 01:32:21,560
快车随时驶至
The Petrol Express will be here in a minute.

1015
01:32:21,650 --> 01:32:23,070
好好享受生命
Have a nice life.

1016
01:32:23,240 --> 01:32:24,900
你的余生
What's left of it.

1017
01:32:28,410 --> 01:32:31,200
你再走近我便扔下手榴弹
You take one step and I'm dropping this grenade.

1018
01:32:36,210 --> 01:32:37,370
扔吧
Drop it.

1019
01:32:59,280 --> 01:33:00,560
没命中
Pegasus missed.

1020
01:33:01,280 --> 01:33:03,270
不是K
It wasn't Kappa.

1021
01:33:03,740 --> 01:33:04,940
天啊
Jesus.

1022
01:33:15,080 --> 01:33:16,990
杀我不会有好处
Shooting me won't do any good.

1023
01:33:17,090 --> 01:33:19,790
他们无法破我的假卫星
ATAC can't get past my ghost satellites.

1024
01:33:19,960 --> 01:33:23,250
亦无法破我的密码程式
And you can't get past my encrypted program.

1025
01:33:23,380 --> 01:33:26,380
你是说我无法把它关掉吗?
You mean to tell me there's no way I can shut that off?

1026
01:33:26,470 --> 01:33:27,580
没办法
No way.

1027
01:33:37,330 --> 01:33:38,850
恢复控制游牧者一号

1028
01:33:39,440 --> 01:33:41,600
我倒没想过
I never thought of that.

1029
01:33:41,780 --> 01:33:43,110
是D
It was Delta.

1030
01:33:48,370 --> 01:33:50,190
瞄准了
We're locked on.

1031
01:33:51,750 --> 01:33:52,690
击中!
Hit it!

1032
01:34:45,550 --> 01:34:48,670
稳定梯子 把直升机停在这儿
Hold the ladder. And keep this chopper right here.

1033
01:35:41,560 --> 01:35:42,760
我从没怀疑你
I never doubted you.

1034
01:35:42,860 --> 01:35:44,560
你有的
Oh, yes, you did.

1035
01:35:45,070 --> 01:35:47,940
这是很动人的时刻
This is a real sweet Hallmark moment, but...

1036
01:35:48,740 --> 01:35:51,110
但我们可以回家去了吗 凯西叔
...can we go home now, Uncle Casey?

1037
01:35:53,370 --> 01:35:56,070
这是505NM直升机
This is Helo 505 November-Mike.

1038
01:35:56,910 --> 01:35:59,660
有讯息 我转过来
Sir, there's a message coming in. I'll patch it through.

1039
01:35:59,750 --> 01:36:00,990
我是雷贝克
This is Casey Ryback.

1040
01:36:01,080 --> 01:36:02,710
人质安全
The hostages are safe.


